&lt;h2 id="計算機單位與轉換">計算機單位與轉換：&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">1 Byte = 8 bit
